title: NOAA, Precipitation Hazards, USA, 9/2/2008
name: NOAA, Precipitation Hazards, USA, 9/2/2008
description:
This shapefile consists of the precipitation hazards for the CPC U.S. Hazards Assessment
The purpose of this product is to denote areas where heavy precipitation could lead to flooding conditions. In addition, areas that have a chance of heavy winter precipitation are also denoted.
A new Hazards forecast is produced every Monday-Friday
This forecast is valid for Days 3-14 after the forecast date, which is denoted in the filename
